30, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_B\", \"score\": 0.9908064165445819, \"rank\": 0.00927888800542301, \"text\": \"Group B\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_B\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_B\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And during competition, Saunders wore the now trademark mask that covers the American's face.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999992171863932, \"rank\": 3.5688854640661174e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Backley, a formerOlympicjavelin silver medalist, repeatedly described to Saunders as 'her' during the live coverage in the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Backley's co-host Jazmin Sawyers duly pointed out that the star identifies as non-binary, and uses different pronouns.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 718, \"end\": 732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jazmin_Sawyers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jazmin Sawyers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2156